Unchecked exception thrown when Index, Table or
 DataColumn operations are invoked (directly, or indirectly as data updates) that
 cannot be completed correctly due to size constraints on the underlying data structures.
 
 For example, the current implementations of RedirectionIndex, required for
 Table.sort(io.deephaven.db.tables.SortPair...), can only support an 32-bit integer number of keys.
